data.title: Rockford IceHogs
data.meta_description: The official website of the Rockford IceHogs. See the latest news, scores, stats and get tickets to every IceHogs home game.
data.text:
2023-24: Signed one-year AHL contract on 8/10/23...Goal and assist in season opener on 10/13/23 at San Jose

2022-23: Traded from BUF to Blackhawks on 3/2/23 and registered eight points (2G, 6A) in 13 games with Chicago

Career: 2019-20: Set NHL career highs in games played, goals, assists, and points...Tabbed one assist in 10 Stanley Cup Playoff games with BOS in the 2020 Stanley Cup Playoffs

College: 2016-17: Hobey Baker Award Finalist as junior...Second Team All-American

Junior: 2015-16: Represented the United States at the U20 World Junior Championships and scored three goals in seven games en route to a Bronze Medal...2013-14: Represented the United States at the U18 World Junior Championships and scored two goals in seven games en route to a Gold Medal
